\" />"},{"pid":"1499f165b67f3275cde62c13cc2a997e0671edcf","tid":305842,"uid":33357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T05:39:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>煙霧感應器放角落咁可疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能唔放角落個角度影唔到"},{"pid":"7acb2ef730e53589c261b007c9b5224ff549b5f4","tid":305842,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T05:40:38.000Z","msg":"Airbnb 真係不了<br />\n<br />\n做野又好 <br />\n旅行又好"},{"pid":"a34ecbaa9e4a146c68a90ccaa1e0b07d7316a33b","tid":305842,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T14:02:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}